nt|^b@2^z@3|va|5|at|We have now defined ways to handle just about any kind of major 2-suiter that you could ever be dealt opposite a 1NT opening bid. The SAYC bidding system has sequences for bidding 5-5 and 5-4 hands in the signoff, invitational, and game forcing ranges. Before we move on, here are a few more points that should be mentioned:

